{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act50side", "eventName": "泡影苍霆", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "TD-1", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "硬壳下的胆小鬼", "storyInfo": "梓兰和空爆将信将疑地跟着自称宝巫迦——和泡普卡一模一样的女孩来到泡影国的都城，转眼却被推举为“异兽猎人”......", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "53_g16_sunnyday_L1/53_g16_sunnyday_R1/53_g16_sunnyday_L2/53_g16_sunnyday_R2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "yFrom": 360.0, "yTo": 720.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "此地乃是名为“泡影国”的国家，吾等世代以狩猎为生。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "而扰乱这片土地安宁的，是每隔十年左右，从“御轮”之中降临的“异兽”，以及“异兽”带来的“诅咒”。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "这正是“御轮”给吾等的“试炼”。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "泡影国的历代国主，也就是吾的祖先们，作为“御轮”之巫女，世代肩负着消除“诅咒”，狩猎“异兽”的责任。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刚才那种冒着黑气的野兽，就是“异兽”吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，那只是受到“诅咒”影响的野兽，被“诅咒”影响的野兽，会变得十分凶暴。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“异兽”是极为强大的野兽，远不是受“诅咒”的野兽可以比拟的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果放任被“诅咒”的野兽不管，就有可能让“诅咒”蔓延，同样变成一个棘手的问题。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你刚才说，你要找的是我们，这和我们有什么关系？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每隔十年，从“御轮”中降临的，不只有“异兽”和“诅咒”，还会有两位“异兽猎人”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一代的“异兽猎人”，都会和国主一起接受“试炼”，狩猎“异兽”，解除“诅咒”，为这片土地带来短暂的安宁。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，也就是说，是我们两个？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是搞错了？我们两个根本不是什么“异兽猎人”......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不会错的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身为国主一脉，吾等与“御轮”有着奇妙的联系，近日，吾已经感觉到它有异动，这才出门寻找。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而两位无论是穿着还是刚见面时使用的语言，都不是吾熟悉的东西......两位一定是“御轮”送来的“异兽猎人”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为什么你们非要接受这所谓的“试炼”不可？听起来它对你们毫无好处。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的，“试炼”对吾等而言，既是挑战，也是馈赠。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行天之谕，狩地之兽。这正是泡影国千百年来恪守的格言。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......过去的“异兽猎人”都怎么样了？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在完成“异兽”狩猎后，国主会吸收“异兽”的“诅咒”，重新开启“御轮”，他们大多选择返回自己的故土，但也有少数人留了下来。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡影国的史书中，记载着每一代“异兽猎人”的生平。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "空爆", "content": "哦，也就是说，只要我们解决这个叫“异兽”的家伙，就能回去了，"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "空爆", "content": "那还挺方便的嘛，梓兰姐。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有这么简单的事......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "请放心，吾不会强迫两位立刻接受这些事情。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面就是都城了，两位有什么问题，进城了再说也不迟。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g1_impermanence_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#3", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#3"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "异邦的旅人，欢迎来到泡影国的都城——泡影城。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本国周围竹林环绕，常常有旅人在其中迷路，而越过竹林，则是......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "两位，怎么了？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是什么......？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪个？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，就是，远处的那个啊。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，如果只是泡影城中呈现的光景，梓兰反而并不会感到惊讶。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，现在出现在她们眼前的事物，是连空爆都会察觉到异常的程度——"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在泡影城的远处，一道金属色泽的拱门静静地矗立在雪山之上。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们难道不会觉得奇怪吗？这么大一道钢铁拱门......", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "钢铁拱门？真是奇怪的称呼。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是“御轮”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“御轮”......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，“御轮”将“异兽”送到了这里，但也将两位这样的“异兽猎人”送了过来。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰抬头，凝视着所谓的“御轮”。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "日光倾泻而下，落在拱门表面那些细密如蛛丝的雕纹上，霎时反射出千百缕虹彩。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "远远看去，就像是一道钢铁“彩虹”，宏伟而又神圣。然而，这座美丽的“彩虹”，不知为何，却令她感到十分不安。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也难怪两位感到惊讶。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“御轮”是吾国的国器，是吾等的祖先从千万年前传下来的遗物，并非现在所造。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原来如此。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果两位对“御轮”感兴趣，吾之后可以为你们介绍。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊，想不通的事情太多了，我感觉自己肚子都在叫了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以不用为饿了找借口的。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......走吧，反正谜团这么多，也不差这一个了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g1_impermanence_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快看，是宝巫迦陛下！", "name": "泡影国百姓A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下的身边有两个人！难道说——", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，梓兰姐，你看，居民们往这边聚集起来了......我们这样的人果然很少见吧。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨，你们好啊！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......算了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，这两位难道就是“异兽猎人”吗？", "name": "泡影国百姓A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）宝巫迦......陛下，有些事情还不明朗，目前还是不要给他们错误的期待吧？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，既然“异兽猎人”来了，也就是说，这个十年的“试炼”依然正常举行，是吗？", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.0, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）陛下？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......各位国民，如你们所见，这两位正是这一轮“试炼”的“异兽猎人”！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了......", "name": "泡影国百姓A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明保佑，我们没有被抛弃......", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位国民，十年前，“雷之主”降临人间。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼时，作为“异兽猎人”降临的政宗大人和义经大人与前代国主，也就是吾的母亲共同前往挑战“雷之主”，然而——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母亲没有能够狩猎“雷之主”，消失在了狩猎之中，政宗大人和义经大人也身受重伤。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这在泡影国的历史上闻所未闻，史书上从未记载，未能完成“试炼”会发生什么......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼时，全国上下一片混乱。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，今天，一切已经明朗——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“御轮”并没有抛弃吾等！新的“异兽猎人”来了！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们真的是“异兽猎人”吗？", "name": "泡影国百姓A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#5"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们一定很强大吧？", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，那当然！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾向诸位保证，吾将会继承母亲的遗志，和这两位“异兽猎人”一起，前往讨伐这一轮的“异兽”，完成这一轮试炼。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不仅如此——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "时至今日，“雷之主”和它带来的“诅咒”依然在泡影国的周边肆虐。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼时，吾尚且年幼，既无法向各位许下承诺，也无法为母亲报仇。在吾心中，“雷之主”也像是一根刺一样无法拔去。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾一直有一个愿望，现在，吾可以说了——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在完成这轮的“异兽”狩猎之后，吾将会前往狩猎“雷之主”......完成母亲未竟的职责，将和平重新带回泡影国！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了......我就知道，宝巫迦陛下会想办法的！宝巫迦陛下万岁！", "name": "泡影国百姓A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别高兴得太早，别忘了前代那时候——", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是这样，陛下如此年幼，已经这么懂事，难道不值得我们欣慰吗？宝巫迦陛下万岁！", "name": "泡影国百姓C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啧，我又不是在怀疑陛下！", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......宝巫迦陛下万岁！", "name": "泡影国百姓B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2109_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#3"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 60.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，别、别推我！我的衣服！别把我抛起来！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#3"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，他们把我们当英雄欸！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但这和刚才说的不一样——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，这么说也是欸。哈哈，没想到，我们也有被泡普卡欺骗的一天。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，也不知道谁总是说，希望泡普卡能自立一点呢——", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "闭嘴！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "false", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对不起，吾算计了两位。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，也没那么严重啦。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我还挺喜欢被当成英雄的感觉哦。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，梓兰姐跟我不一样，她最受不了这种事了，所以你要道歉的话，要好好向梓兰姐道歉哦。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰小姐——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，这个眼泪汪汪的表情，果然是本人。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看来你不用道歉了。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，你刚才肯定在想，“泡普卡终于长大了”之类的对吧？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "闭嘴。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#5"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正是有原因的，对吧？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "两位毫无疑问是“异兽猎人”，并且，消灭“异兽”后，就能通过“御轮”返回两位的家园，这点吾绝没有欺骗两位。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，若是往常，吾作为国主，绝不会以此等手段，几乎是强迫两位接受使命。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此事，要从前代说起......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_darkcloud_thunder", "layer": 1.0, "x": 0.0, "xto": 0.0, "y": 140.0, "movetime": 25.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年前降临的那头“异兽”......是笼罩在泡影国所有人头顶的一场噩梦。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今被称作“雷之主”的那头“异兽”，它的力量与敏捷都远胜曾经的“异兽”，不仅如此，它还拥有能够自如地操控雷电的能力。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如吾方才在广场所说的那样......"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前代国主，也就是吾的母亲，并没有完成“异兽”狩猎，不仅如此，母亲还消失在了狩猎之中。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而这在本国历史上，是前所未有的。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“异兽”不死，则“诅咒”不绝。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在过去的十年中，吾等不得不时刻面临着“雷之主”的侵扰，以及受到“诅咒”的野兽们愈发频繁的袭击......"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更让人恐惧的是——"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都不知所措，不知道“御轮”是否会降下惩罚，又或者，是否会发生一些意料之外的事......"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g1_impermanence_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而对吾而言......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾只有一个愿望，那就是——狩猎“雷之主”，为母亲复仇，也为国家带来安宁。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "听起来，有人拦着你这么做？你是国主，谁敢？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜，是吗？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......没错。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母亲去世后，他代替年幼的吾主持国政，这十年间，他做了许多事。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他将猎人们全部召入宫中，宣布他们的身份从猎人转为武士，然后将他们一一登记，编制成狩猎团，由他亲自管理。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是从那时起，他才有了将军这个名号。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，国民们已经习惯了不能自由狩猎的生活，但吾等至少在“雷之主”的阴影下活了下来。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾承认，没有他，就稳不住民心，或许，泡影国也无法撑到今天。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，面对将吾国逼至这等境地的罪魁祸首——“雷之主”，他却从来没有狩猎它的想法，甚至禁止吾挑战它。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为什么？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他总是说，时候未到。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那什么时候是时候到了？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他要求吾至少完成三轮“试炼”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三轮试炼......三十年？！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因为母亲在挑战“雷之主”时，已经经历过三轮“试炼”，他便以此来要求吾。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾等不了那么久。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是属于吾的第一次“试炼”，吾要在这次“试炼”中就向他证明，吾有那个能力！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以你才急切地把我们推上了那个位置。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在过去十年中，每一次，吾想要去挑战“雷之主”，他总是会如同鬼魅一般出现在吾的身后，劝告吾。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾不想被看扁，也不愿让十年前的未竟之事一再拖延。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军的随从？你去告诉将军，吾已经找到了“异兽猎人”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军已经知晓了。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根据斥候的消息，都城东方的竹林一带，出现了异常活跃的熔火蜗集团，极有可能是受到了“异兽”的影响。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军的意思是？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然新的“试炼”正常开始，他不会干涉您的行动。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下来，一切有关的情报，我也会直接传递给您。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......知道了，去告诉将军，吾这就动身。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看来，他猜到了你的心思。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是个讨厌的家伙。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，他看起来不打算阻止你。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他总是这样，远远地看着吾，静静地等着吾向他承认，吾做不到。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾绝不会向他认输。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，两位，吾请求你们和吾一同行动，即使不参与狩猎也没关系，吾会解决“异兽”，把两位送回去。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我还有很多问题想要问，但现在，我只有一个问题——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你刚才说，在过去，每一次“异兽”狩猎都成功了......难道在我们之前的所有“异兽猎人”，都接受了这项使命？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他们之中，就没有一个人想过逃跑，或者拒绝？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......并非如此。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事实上，根据记载，一开始，像你这样质疑和拒绝的“异兽猎人”才是多数。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，出于种种原因，他们最终都接受了这项使命，成为了狩猎“异兽”的“异兽猎人”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "史书上是这样记载的——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“异兽猎人”者，非“御轮”之选也。", "x": 200.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n乃其人识己之身，闻己之欲，鉴己之勇，得己之器，遂承己之命也。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}